  "body": "# Problem\r\n\r\nWhile working on issue https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/issues/16119 to fix the Community Overview screen, I noticed the [Information Box component](https://www.figma.com/file/WQZcp6S0EnzxdTL4taoKDv/Design-System-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=2950-58462&t=vn4WsmE1ENMSA6xX-0) had lots of subtle inconsistencies.\r\n\r\nUpon further inspection we can see the component is incorrectly implemented.\r\n\r\n- It reuses the Info Message component ([Figma](https://www.figma.com/file/WQZcp6S0EnzxdTL4taoKDv/Design-System-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=2950-43503&t=vn4WsmE1ENMSA6xX-0), [code](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/blob/350303256b0c5f3a5d6c806482eb3a48c32803b5/src/quo2/components/info/information_box.cljs#L80)), but this is incorrect. It's not how the design system is implemented (they're independent) and it causes incorrect spacing between the icon and text.\r\n- The close icon is not right aligned.\r\n- The main button is incorrectly fixed as `primary`, but it can also be `danger`.\r\n\r\nOther problems are more on the technical side because the component was created before the new guidelines were set.\r\n\r\n#### Screenshot with issues\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/46027/2d1ca9bc-61da-427e-9d99-f9c8341a315d\" height=\"600\" />\r\n",
